  "title": "NEW! Compliance and Risk Monitoring Analyst - Fintech (Contract)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Support the rollout and day-to-day running of a regional risk program by establishing processes, controls, and monitoring frameworks</li><li>Analyse data and dashboards to identify merchants with elevated risk, investigate issues, and track program effectiveness</li><li>Manage operational activities including merchant notifications, follow-ups, and billing related to non-compliance</li><li>Partner with internal teams and regional stakeholders to communicate risk findings, provide guidance, and ensure consistent program execution</li><li>Contribute to process improvements, automation initiatives, and tool enhancements to increase efficiency and data quality</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested applicants please send your resume in MS Word format and attention it to Rachel Yeo (R22104385).<br />Shortlisted candidates will be notified<br />Data provided is for recruitment purposes only<br />www.ambition.com.sg<br />EA Registration Number: R22104385<br />Business Registration Number: 200611680D. Licence Number: 10C5117</p>",
